<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.4">
<l>cetta piṇattait teḷiyā torupēy ceṉṟu viralcuṭṭik</l>
<l>katti yuṟumik kaṉalviṭ ṭeṟintu kaṭakkap pāyntupōyp</l>
<l>pattal vayiṟṟaip pataikka mōtip palapē yirintōṭap</l>
<l>pitta vēṭaṅ koṇṭu naṭṭam perumā ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While, as unclear about a dead body one demoness goes, pointing with [her] finger,</l>
<l>howling, growling, hurling fire [and] jumping to cross [it],</l>
<l>beating, so that it throbs, [her] pot belly, many demonesses retreat [and] run,</l>
<l>taking the guise of a madman the great lord is dancing [his] dance.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
